						<summary>

						<p>This is a damaged inscription in Vaṭṭeḻuttu. It records some provision made by one Bāradāyaṉ Brahmaśrīrājaṉ for burning a lamp in the temple of Bhaṭāra and probably for offerings and worship on festival days and for a lamp in a shrine of the goddess (?) The <hi rend="italic">sabhā</hi> of the place seems to have taken this responsibility.</p>						

						</summary>
